funtest.testharness

Class TestHarnessImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • funtest.testharness.TestHarnessImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TestHarness

    public class TestHarnessImpl
extends Object
implements TestHarness
    The TestHarness class provides "the glue" of the test harness. This class handles the loading of a test case, the running of each of the test steps and calling the list of outputters

    codersparks
